<para>
  These classes are used as the <varname>method</varname> parameter in
  <xref linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Image.Modify.Threshold"/>.  They are
  mostly just wrappers around &skimage; methods in <code><ulink
  url="https://scikit-image.org/docs/stable/api/skimage.filters.html"
  mode="external">skimage.filters</ulink></code>.  The classes differ
  in the way in which the threshold value is selected.
</para>

